Prerequisites:
1. Strava for Splunk
2. MLTK
3. Maps+ for Splunk

Install:
1. download and install sports-dashboard.spl
2. download the .svg files from the images folder
3. navigate to the main dashboard, edit it and add them in the items giving an "error retriving kvstore from Image registry"
+ the order from the left to the right: line 1: Ski, Ride, VirtualRide, Swim. Line 2: Hike, Run, Dive, Surf
4. add the .jpg image as a background for the main dashboard

Customization: 
remove / rearrange items according to your needs.
